        "content": "<p>Heap-Hop <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12778#issuecomment-4060535460\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/12778\">issue #12778</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Heap-Hop/wasmtime/commit/c5245c1960cf4e712e3f9dde838b2898ee30011b\">https://github.com/Heap-Hop/wasmtime/commit/c5245c1960cf4e712e3f9dde838b2898ee30011b</a> causes a new failure:<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Heap-Hop/wasmtime/actions/runs/23087440874/job/67066363560#step:22:849\">https://github.com/Heap-Hop/wasmtime/actions/runs/23087440874/job/67066363560#step:22:849</a><br>\nThis might not be a complete fix yet.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 579442272,
